{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.012.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">L\u2019autel de B\u00e9thel et la main de J\u00e9roboam<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. 2 R 23:15-20. Ps 105:14, 15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Voici, un homme de Dieu arriva de Juda \u00e0 B\u00e9thel, par la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, pendant que J\u00e9roboam se tenait \u00e0 l\u2019autel pour br\u00fbler des parfums.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.2","name":"1 Rois 13:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.33","name":"1 Rois 12:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.12.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il cria contre l\u2019autel, par la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il dit: Autel! Autel! Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Voici, il na\u00eetra un fils \u00e0 la maison de David; son nom sera Josias; il immolera sur toi les pr\u00eatres des hauts lieux qui br\u00fblent sur toi des parfums, et l\u2019on br\u00fblera sur toi des ossements d\u2019hommes!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.3","name":"1 Rois 13:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.1","name":"1 Rois 13:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Et le m\u00eame jour il donna un signe, en disant: C\u2019est ici le signe que l\u2019\u00c9ternel a parl\u00e9: Voici, l\u2019autel se fendra, et la cendre qui est dessus sera r\u00e9pandue.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.4","name":"1 Rois 13:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.2","name":"1 Rois 13:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Lorsque le roi entendit la parole que l\u2019homme de Dieu avait cri\u00e9e contre l\u2019autel de B\u00e9thel, il avan\u00e7a la main de dessus l\u2019autel, en disant: Saisissez-le! Et la main que J\u00e9roboam avait \u00e9tendue contre lui devint s\u00e8che, et il ne put la ramener \u00e0 soi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.5","name":"1 Rois 13:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.3","name":"1 Rois 13:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>L\u2019autel se fendit, et la cendre qui \u00e9tait dessus fut r\u00e9pandue, selon le signe qu\u2019avait donn\u00e9 l\u2019homme de Dieu, par la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.6","name":"1 Rois 13:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.4","name":"1 Rois 13:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Alors le roi prit la parole, et dit \u00e0 l\u2019homme de Dieu: Implore l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, et prie pour moi, afin que je puisse retirer ma main. L\u2019homme de Dieu implora l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et le roi put retirer sa main, qui fut comme auparavant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.7","name":"1 Rois 13:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.5","name":"1 Rois 13:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 l\u2019homme de Dieu: Entre avec moi dans la maison, tu prendras quelque nourriture, et je te donnerai un pr\u00e9sent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.8","name":"1 Rois 13:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.6","name":"1 Rois 13:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>L\u2019homme de Dieu dit au roi: Quand tu me donnerais la moiti\u00e9 de ta maison, je n\u2019entrerais pas avec toi. Je ne mangerai point de pain, et je ne boirai point d\u2019eau dans ce lieu-ci;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.9","name":"1 Rois 13:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.7","name":"1 Rois 13:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>car cet ordre m\u2019a \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9, par la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Tu ne mangeras point de pain et tu ne boiras point d\u2019eau, et tu ne prendras pas \u00e0 ton retour le chemin par lequel tu seras all\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.10","name":"1 Rois 13:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.8","name":"1 Rois 13:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Et il s\u2019en alla par un autre chemin, il ne prit pas \u00e0 son retour le chemin par lequel il \u00e9tait venu \u00e0 B\u00e9thel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.11","name":"1 Rois 13:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.9","name":"1 Rois 13:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Un proph\u00e8te tu\u00e9 par un lion<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-32: cf. 1 R 20:35, 36. Ga 1:6-8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Or il y avait un vieux proph\u00e8te qui demeurait \u00e0 B\u00e9thel. Ses fils vinrent lui raconter toutes les choses que l\u2019homme de Dieu avait faites \u00e0 B\u00e9thel ce jour-l\u00e0, et les paroles qu\u2019il avait dites au roi. Lorsqu\u2019ils en eurent fait le r\u00e9cit \u00e0 leur p\u00e8re,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.12","name":"1 Rois 13:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.10","name":"1 Rois 13:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>il leur dit: Par quel chemin s\u2019en est-il all\u00e9? Ses fils avaient vu par quel chemin s\u2019en \u00e9tait all\u00e9 l\u2019homme de Dieu qui \u00e9tait venu de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.13","name":"1 Rois 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.11","name":"1 Rois 13:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et il dit \u00e0 ses fils: Sellez-moi l\u2019\u00e2ne. Ils lui sell\u00e8rent l\u2019\u00e2ne, et il monta dessus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.14","name":"1 Rois 13:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.12","name":"1 Rois 13:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il alla apr\u00e8s l\u2019homme de Dieu, et il le trouva assis sous un t\u00e9r\u00e9binthe. Il lui dit: Es-tu l\u2019homme de Dieu qui est venu de Juda? Il r\u00e9pondit: Je le suis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.15","name":"1 Rois 13:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.13","name":"1 Rois 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Alors il lui dit: Viens avec moi \u00e0 la maison, et tu prendras quelque nourriture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.16","name":"1 Rois 13:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.14","name":"1 Rois 13:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Mais il r\u00e9pondit: Je ne puis ni retourner avec toi, ni entrer chez toi. Je ne mangerai point de pain, je ne boirai point d\u2019eau avec toi en ce lieu-ci;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.17","name":"1 Rois 13:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.15","name":"1 Rois 13:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>car il m\u2019a \u00e9t\u00e9 dit, par la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Tu n\u2019y mangeras point de pain et tu n\u2019y boiras point d\u2019eau, et tu ne prendras pas \u00e0 ton retour le chemin par lequel tu seras all\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.18","name":"1 Rois 13:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.16","name":"1 Rois 13:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et il lui dit: Moi aussi, je suis proph\u00e8te comme toi; et un ange m\u2019a parl\u00e9 de la part de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et m\u2019a dit: Ram\u00e8ne-le avec toi dans ta maison, et qu\u2019il mange du pain et boive de l\u2019eau. Il lui mentait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.19","name":"1 Rois 13:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.17","name":"1 Rois 13:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>L\u2019homme de Dieu retourna avec lui, et il mangea du pain et but de l\u2019eau dans sa maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.20","name":"1 Rois 13:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.18","name":"1 Rois 13:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Comme ils \u00e9taient assis \u00e0 table, la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut adress\u00e9e au proph\u00e8te qui l\u2019avait ramen\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.21","name":"1 Rois 13:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.19","name":"1 Rois 13:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et il cria \u00e0 l\u2019homme de Dieu qui \u00e9tait venu de Juda: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Parce que tu as \u00e9t\u00e9 rebelle \u00e0 l\u2019ordre de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et que tu n\u2019as pas observ\u00e9 le commandement que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, t\u2019avait donn\u00e9;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.22","name":"1 Rois 13:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.20","name":"1 Rois 13:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>parce que tu es retourn\u00e9, et que tu as mang\u00e9 du pain et bu de l\u2019eau dans le lieu dont il t\u2019avait dit: Tu n\u2019y mangeras point de pain et tu n\u2019y boiras point d\u2019eau, ton cadavre n\u2019entrera pas dans le s\u00e9pulcre de tes p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.23","name":"1 Rois 13:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.21","name":"1 Rois 13:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Et quand le proph\u00e8te qu\u2019il avait ramen\u00e9 eut mang\u00e9 du pain et qu\u2019il eut bu de l\u2019eau, il sella l\u2019\u00e2ne pour lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.24","name":"1 Rois 13:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.22","name":"1 Rois 13:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>L\u2019homme de Dieu s\u2019en alla: et il fut rencontr\u00e9 dans le chemin par un lion qui le tua. Son cadavre \u00e9tait \u00e9tendu dans le chemin; l\u2019\u00e2ne resta pr\u00e8s de lui, et le lion se tint \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 du cadavre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.25","name":"1 Rois 13:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.23","name":"1 Rois 13:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Et voici, des gens qui passaient virent le cadavre \u00e9tendu dans le chemin et le lion se tenant \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 du cadavre; et ils en parl\u00e8rent \u00e0 leur arriv\u00e9e dans la ville o\u00f9 demeurait le vieux proph\u00e8te.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.26","name":"1 Rois 13:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.24","name":"1 Rois 13:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Lorsque le proph\u00e8te qui avait ramen\u00e9 du chemin l\u2019homme de Dieu l\u2019eut appris, il dit: C\u2019est l\u2019homme de Dieu qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 rebelle \u00e0 l\u2019ordre de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et l\u2019\u00c9ternel l\u2019a livr\u00e9 au lion, qui l\u2019a d\u00e9chir\u00e9 et l\u2019a fait mourir, selon la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel lui avait dite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.27","name":"1 Rois 13:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.25","name":"1 Rois 13:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Puis, s\u2019adressant \u00e0 ses fils, il dit: Sellez-moi l\u2019\u00e2ne. Ils le sell\u00e8rent,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.28","name":"1 Rois 13:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.26","name":"1 Rois 13:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>et il partit. Il trouva le cadavre \u00e9tendu dans le chemin, et l\u2019\u00e2ne et le lion qui se tenaient \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 du cadavre. Le lion n\u2019avait pas d\u00e9vor\u00e9 le cadavre et n\u2019avait pas d\u00e9chir\u00e9 l\u2019\u00e2ne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.29","name":"1 Rois 13:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.27","name":"1 Rois 13:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Le proph\u00e8te releva le cadavre de l\u2019homme de Dieu, le pla\u00e7a sur l\u2019\u00e2ne, et le ramena; et le vieux proph\u00e8te rentra dans la ville pour le pleurer et pour l\u2019enterrer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.30","name":"1 Rois 13:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.28","name":"1 Rois 13:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Il mit son cadavre dans le s\u00e9pulcre, et l\u2019on pleura sur lui, en disant: H\u00e9las, mon fr\u00e8re!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.31","name":"1 Rois 13:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.29","name":"1 Rois 13:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s l\u2019avoir enterr\u00e9, il dit \u00e0 ses fils: Quand je serai mort, vous m\u2019enterrerez dans le s\u00e9pulcre o\u00f9 est enterr\u00e9 l\u2019homme de Dieu, vous d\u00e9poserez mes os \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de ses os.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.32","name":"1 Rois 13:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.30","name":"1 Rois 13:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Car elle s\u2019accomplira, la parole qu\u2019il a cri\u00e9e, de la part de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, contre l\u2019autel de B\u00e9thel et contre toutes les maisons des hauts lieux qui sont dans les villes de Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.33","name":"1 Rois 13:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.31","name":"1 Rois 13:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.034,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 33-34: cf. 1 R 14:7-10; 15:25-30. Pr 1:24, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s cet \u00e9v\u00e9nement, J\u00e9roboam ne se d\u00e9tourna point de sa mauvaise voie. Il cr\u00e9a de nouveau des pr\u00eatres des hauts lieux pris parmi tout le peuple; quiconque en avait le d\u00e9sir, il le consacrait pr\u00eatre des hauts lieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.34","name":"1 Rois 13:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.32","name":"1 Rois 13:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.34","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 13:34","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.13.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Ce fut l\u00e0 une occasion de p\u00e9ch\u00e9 pour la maison de J\u00e9roboam, et c\u2019est pour cela qu\u2019elle a \u00e9t\u00e9 extermin\u00e9e et d\u00e9truite de dessus la face de la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13","name":"1 Rois 13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.1","name":"1 Rois 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.33","name":"1 Rois 13:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fba30ee30.58146113');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba30ee30.58146113\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fba30ee30.58146113","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fba30ee30.58146113'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba30ee30.58146113\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}